Charlie. wake up.
Charlie. wake...

1207
01:01:06.412 --> 01:01:08.623
Charlie. wake up!

1208
01:01:08.706 --> 01:01:10.041
I've been trying
to call Erik all night.

1209
01:01:10.124 --> 01:01:11.376
He's not answering me.

1210
01:01:11.459 --> 01:01:13.753
I don't know where he is.
I'm worried.

1211
01:01:13.836 --> 01:01:15.171
I'm sure he's fine.

1212
