1287
01:03:54.914 --> 01:03:55.414
-Mwah!
-[Stefani] Erik. get away!

1288
01:03:55.498 --> 01:03:57.166
Stop!

1289
01:03:57.250 --> 01:03:59.085
-[Erik] You like that?
